クラス JEditActionContext<F extends JEditAbstractEditAction,E extends JEditActionSet<F>>

java.lang.Object
  org.gjt.sp.jedit.JEditActionContext<F,E>
直系の既知のサブクラス:
ActionContext
public abstract class JEditActionContext<F extends JEditAbstractEditAction,E extends JEditActionSet<F>>
extends java.lang.Object

Manages a collection of action sets. There are two instances of this class in jEdit:

  • jEdit.getActionContext() - editor actions
  • VFSBrowser.getActionContext() - browser actions

導入されたバージョン:
jEdit 4.3pre13
バージョン:
